Take a look inside young NBA star Ja Morant’s $3M home in Eads, Tenn

Basketball Andree · 22/08/2023

﻿Ja Morant is the current franchise icon for the Memphis Grizzlies. Since joining the NBA, Morant has made his presence known by receiving the Rookie of the Year and Most Improved Player of the Year awards. However, his public image took a significant blow in 2023 after he displayed a firearm twice on social media. The initial incident resulted in a suspension of eight games. The second incident resulted in a suspension of 25 games.
